favorites.name: Haircalf Bomber Jacket
favorites.description: A haircalf W. Anzevino + A. Getty bomber jacket with interior leather trim. Snap placket with tonal metal hardware. 2 front pockets. Contrast ribbing at the collar, hem, and cuffs.

favorites.name: Green Squares Bomber Jacket
favorites.description: This fiber-filled Anzevino + Getty bomber jacket has lamé squares to create a unique grid effect. Contrast, ribbed edges bring the avant-garde piece back to its sporty roots. Zip closure. 2 welt pockets. Quilted lining.

favorites.name: Margiela Tee
favorites.description: Your life may be upside-down and this T-shirt will just follow that assuring that. Constructed from pure cotton, this embroidered upside-down logo T-shirt from Maison Margiela is adorned with a twisted logo. At least, you will be the coolest guy around the block anyway. Featuring a round neck, short sleeves, a straight hem and an embroidered upside-down logo.

favorites.name: Candy
favorites.description: Just a delicious candy. Almost for free. Mostly used for us to test payments.

favorites.name: Chuck Taylor All Star
favorites.description: From simple beginnings on the basketball court, Converse sneakers have reached iconic status. With a spirit of originality and rebellion, classic Chuck Taylor Converse All Star high-tops receive a constant update with fresh color ways and prints introduced each season; while Converse's clothing collection of tanks, tees and hoodies continues to mirror their relaxed, contemporary-cool vibe.

favorites.name: JuunJ Rob Ryan Pullover
favorites.description:
Neoprene sweatshirt from Junn.J’s collaboration with Rob Ryan. Silver foil and embroidery emphasize the black and white graphics and text on this pullover.
